HOW TO TEST XSLT-BLOG:
----------------------
* execute script gener_article.pl to generate specific
  number of articles (all articles will be generate in
  directory ./xml/articles/)
* execute scipt gener_article_list.pl to generate article
  list for specific number of articles and categories
  (article list will be generate in directory./xml)
* copy generated articles into the directory
   ../xml/articles/
* copy generated article list into the directory ../xml/
